tak menampakkan dirinya lagi.

948
01:43:59,566 --> 01:44:00,670
Kenapa?

949
01:44:03,837 --> 01:44:05,874
Sekarang aku sendirian lagi.

950
01:44:11,078 --> 01:44:12,523
Aku kedinginan.

951
